org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HRM.HwLogical.HwCommunication

Interface HwBus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommunicationMedia, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwCommunicationResource, HwMedia, HwResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ProcessingResource, Resource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwBusImpl

    public interface HwBus
extends HwMedia
    A representation of the model object 'Hw Bus'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Adress Width
    • Word Width
    • Is Synchronous
    • Is Serial
    See Also:
    HwCommunicationPackage.getHwBus()
